Generate Data from a Multivariate Normal Distribution following a Simple Mediation Model

Source: R/mvn_dat_complete.R
mvn_dat.Rd

Generate Data from a Multivariate Normal Distribution following a Simple Mediation Model

mvn_dat(taskid)

Arguments

taskid

Numeric. Task ID.

See also

Other multivariate normal data functions: mvn_dat_mar_10_simulation(), mvn_dat_mar_10_task(), mvn_dat_mar_10(), mvn_dat_mar_20_simulation(), mvn_dat_mar_20_task(), mvn_dat_mar_20(), mvn_dat_mar_30_simulation(), mvn_dat_mar_30_task(), mvn_dat_mar_30(), mvn_dat_mar_50_simulation(), mvn_dat_mar_50_task(), mvn_dat_mar_50(), mvn_dat_mar_simulation(), mvn_dat_mar_task(), mvn_dat_mar(), mvn_dat_mcar_10_simulation(), mvn_dat_mcar_10_task(), mvn_dat_mcar_10(), mvn_dat_mcar_20_simulation(), mvn_dat_mcar_20_task(), mvn_dat_mcar_20(), mvn_dat_mcar_30_simulation(), mvn_dat_mcar_30_task(), mvn_dat_mcar_30(), mvn_dat_mcar_50_simulation(), mvn_dat_mcar_50_task(), mvn_dat_mcar_50(), mvn_dat_mcar_simulation(), mvn_dat_mcar_task(), mvn_dat_mcar(), mvn_dat_mnar_10_simulation(), mvn_dat_mnar_10_task(), mvn_dat_mnar_10(), mvn_dat_mnar_20_simulation(), mvn_dat_mnar_20_task(), mvn_dat_mnar_20(), mvn_dat_mnar_30_simulation(), mvn_dat_mnar_30_task(), mvn_dat_mnar_30(), mvn_dat_mnar_50_simulation(), mvn_dat_mnar_50_task(), mvn_dat_mnar_50(), mvn_dat_mnar_simulation(), mvn_dat_mnar_task(), mvn_dat_mnar(), mvn_dat_simulation(), mvn_dat_task(), mvn(), setparamsmvn(), useparamsmvn()

Examples

data <- mvn_dat(taskid = 1)
fit.ols(data, minimal = TRUE)
#> [1] 0.5319165
fit.ols(data, minimal = TRUE, std = TRUE)
